next
  Summary: default min_minutes raised to 120, MCM string clarifications, readme restructure
  MCM:
    Changed: default min_minutes raised from 60 to 120 (refill fires two game hours after the last advance)
    Changed: advances slider renamed from "Advances to refill" to "Advances to floor"; description rewritten to attribute the spawn to the engine's try_respawn
